data.description: If you're in search of a spacious home in the Putnam City school district, look no further. The current owners have painstakingly updated this property with new floors, a fresh coat of paint, a renovated hall bathroom, upgraded fixtures, and more. You'll find an abundance of cabinets throughout the house, offering ample storage solutions. The master bedroom impressively features two closets for your convenience. The kitchen, complete with granite countertops and ceramic tile in both the kitchen and entryway, ensures a seamless experience for cooking and family entertainment. Appliances stay in current condition. Additionally, the gas stove in the family room not only adds warmth and coziness but also contributes to reduced utility bills during the winter months. For added peace of mind, there's an interior above-ground storm shelter, providing safety during stormy seasons. When summer arrives, the backyard transforms into an oasis, featuring an almost-new pool and deck. Furthermore, a 10x20 insulated workshop comes equipped with electricity and AC. This property offers easy access to a variety of amenities, including shopping centers, restaurants, and parks. Effortless commuting to other parts of the city is facilitated by the nearby major highways. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming property your own.
